        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p><strong>Dedicated support via email, Slack, and phone.</strong></p>
          <p>Support tiers:</p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Standard (included):</strong> Email/Slack support, 24-hour response time, knowledge base access</li>
            <li><strong>Priority:</strong> Phone support, 4-hour response time, dedicated account manager</li>
